          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Teachers are the best Asset of this school.\nEnvironment has changed a lot from past. Principal and Head mistress are putting their best to make everything in order. This gives us a sense that our kid is in safe hands.\nSchool administration is very co-operative as well.\nImportant thing is school is giving fair chance to underprivileged kids and that's a great contribution to the society and value instilling example for kids.\nSupporting staff is also religiously doing their job and helping our kids.\nSome improvements/addition in sports curriculum needed else all is good.\nI think this is the best school I can get for my kid.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
