            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Both my daughters studied in this school for 3 years before we got transferred to South India. I always found the school approachable, Head mistress and all staff responded as needed. Studies were good and the school has a large play ground where kids can play. Overall I rate this school very good.",
